data.description: Contract Pending - On market for back up offers only. Ranch buyers will be impressed by this move in ready townhome. 3 BR, 3 Bth, 2 Car Garage. All appliances included. Fresh interior paint, new entry tile, and newer carpet. Basement features a Rec Room with built in cabinets, half bath, huge storage room with a work bench. Fenced yard has a sprinkler system. Long, level driveway. Vaulted ceilings in the Living Room/Dining Room. Gas log fireplace. 3 main floor bedrooms. The Primary BR has a walk in closet and 3/4 bath. A main floor laundry for convenience. Gorgeous kitchen with tile floor, newer appliances and, tons of cabinets. Vinyl exterior siding, and clad windows. No HOA. Priced to sell fast!
